  <brief_title>A Clinical Study of GRC 8200 in Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 12-week Randomized, Double-blind, Parallel Group, Placebo-controlled Study to Evaluate Safety, Tolerability, and Efficacy of GRC 8200, a New Oral DPP -IV Inhibitor, in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
