  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is aimed at evaluating efficacy and safety of GRC 8200 in type 2 diabetes mellitus
      patients.

      The study involves six weeks of wash out period and two weeks run in period for patients
      currently on mono-therapy and a two week run in period only for drug naïve patients.

      This is a placebo controlled study. One of the five treatment arms is placebo. The duration
      of treatment is 12 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
